# ===========================================================================
# Custom Ollama Modelfile — ReactiveAgents runtime model (s8/b8 swap to E4B)
# Base: batiai/gemma4-e4b:q4 (Google Gemma 4 edge E4B, TEXT-ONLY Q4, ~4.8 GB)
# Build:  ollama create gemma4-e4b-candidate-ctx32k -f Modelfile.gemma4-e4b-candidate-ctx32k
#
# This is the SHIP-PATH model (DEFAULT_MODEL in llm_framework/transport.py). It
# replaces gemma4-e2b-agent (d42, retired): s10/s11 measured E4B the only
# fit-passing upgrade beating e2b — better instruction-following + strict-format,
# no deep-research over-routing — while still fitting the 6 GB RTX 4050 at 0%
# offload. Same gemma4 family/renderer as e2b, so CoT lands in message.thinking
# (think=True) with clean fenced JSON in content (d25 revalidated on E4B).
#
# Pull the COMMUNITY TEXT-ONLY base (batiai/gemma4-e4b:q4, ~4.8 GB), NOT the
# official ~9.6 GB text+image+audio tag (its mmproj projector wastes ~0.86 GB of
# dead VRAM for text work). gemma4-e2b's Modelfile / tag are left UNTOUCHED.
# ===========================================================================
FROM batiai/gemma4-e4b:q4

# gemma4 renderer/parser so think=True CoT lands in message.thinking, exactly
# like e2b (the transport's JSON-extraction interceptor + thinking-capture rely
# on this shape — d25).
TEMPLATE {{ .Prompt }}
RENDERER gemma4
PARSER gemma4
PARAMETER stop <turn|>

# --- d36 baseline (pinned) -------------------------------------------------
# num_ctx 32768: window OVERFLOW (not VRAM) is the failure mode — a realistic
# ~18.4k-token deep-research synthesize prompt overflows 8192/16384 (truncated ->
# empty thinking -> thin report, the o4 root cause); 32768 fits the full prompt
# WITH room for CoT + substantive output. SWA keeps KV cheap so 32768 is safe on
# 6 GB. temperature 0 is the measured-best for E4B's deterministic/structured/
# write work (s11 sweep: 0.928 vs 0.685 @0.3, reproduced 3x); per-call sites may
# override num_predict/temperature over HTTP /api options.
PARAMETER num_ctx 32768
PARAMETER temperature 0
PARAMETER top_p 0.95
PARAMETER top_k 64
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.0

# --- Output budget ---------------------------------------------------------
# Modelfile floor only; reasoned call sites RAISE num_predict to >=4096 over HTTP
# (with think=True the CoT competes with content; <=512 -> empty content, d6).
PARAMETER num_predict 1024

# --- System prompt (neutral fallback) --------------------------------------
# The ReactiveAgents runtime sends its OWN system message per task (the universal
# agent identity + planner factory / composed spec rulesets), which Ollama uses
# in preference to this default — so this is just a sane baseline for a bare
# /api/generate warm call and does NOT fight the agent.
SYSTEM """You are the local reasoning model for the ReactiveAgents app. Be precise and follow the caller's output-format instructions exactly."""

# --- Runtime knobs that are NOT Modelfile params (set by server/transport) --
# * think        -> request field on /api/chat (think=false on structured calls,
#                   think=true on reasoned calls). Not bakeable.
# * keep_alive   -> request field; the app passes -1 (RESIDENT, d36) since the GPU
#                   is gemma's SOLE consumer (kills per-call reload thrash). Not bakeable.
# * Server env (on `ollama serve`): OLLAMA_FLASH_ATTENTION=1, OLLAMA_NUM_PARALLEL=1,
#   OLLAMA_MAX_LOADED_MODELS=1. Leave KV cache at default f16.
